<bibRefCitation author="Warner" box="[331,485,694,718]" pageId="9" pageNumber="376" refString="Warner, G. F. (1981) Species descriptions and ecological observations of black corals (Antipatharia) from Trinidad. Bulletin of Marine Science, 31, 147 - 163." type="journal article" year="1981">Warner, 1981</bibRefCitation>
). The Bermudan specimens examined as part of this study were collected at a depths ranging between 
